These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
House: cape-cod, futuristic
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, golf
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, montecristo
City: london, paris
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, grapefruit
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, fuchsia
1. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person eating raspberry is the person traveling to paris##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| House      | futuristic     | cape-cod       |
| Flower         | bellflower   | sunflower     |
| Sport           | cycling | golf   |
| Cigar   | montecristo   | siglo  |
| City   | paris | london |
| Food           | raspberry      | grapefruit     |
| Color     | fuchsia    | emerald   |

