.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, musical
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, tomato
City: paris, liverpool
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, rugby
2 different games are played: poker, whist
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, november
1. the person eating tomato is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
5. the person watching horror movies is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Movie-Genre      | horror    | musical |
| Cigar         | blend        | old-henry  |
| Food           | artichoke | tomato  |
| City   | liverpool            | paris    |
| Sport   | skateboarding     | rugby   |
| Game           | poker         | whist    |
| Birthday     | april           | november      |

